title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

Parking meters in Norwalk, Connecticut, offer: “15 min for each nickel; 30 min for each dime; and for convenience, one hour for one quarter.” [Submitted by Charles King, Jr., Wilton, Connecticut.]
